==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chimerical
<hw>Chi*mer"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Merely
imaginary; fanciful; fantastic; wildly or vainly conceived; having, or
capable of having, no existence except in thought; <as>as,
<ex>chimerical</ex> projects</as>.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Imaginary; fanciful; fantastic; wild; unfounded;
vain; deceitful; delusive.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chimerically</ent>⟦br⟧
